1
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,970
[Blind Woman]

2
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,900
[Episode 4: Come on, Jump Down]

3
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:29,960
Miss Lin.

4
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:31,440
Please be at ease.

5
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,640
I'm a doctor.

6
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,390
I will never cross any boundaries.

7
00:00:35,430 --> 00:00:36,110
Okay.

8
00:00:46,860 --> 00:00:47,730
There's no anesthetic here,

9
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:48,920
so bear with it.

10
00:01:01,630 --> 00:01:03,030
Hang in there. I'm almost finished.

11
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:29,030
♫The wind and rain shake the tender branches♫

12
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:31,780
♫Dark clouds trap the sunset's glow♫

13
00:01:31,810 --> 00:01:35,650
♫No one knows when the skies will clear♫

14
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,720
♫Even the birds have fallen silent♫

15
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,200
She's having a fever.

16
00:01:38,740 --> 00:01:42,580
♫Darkness seems to swallow me whole♫

17
00:01:42,850 --> 00:01:44,770
♫Who can purify my soul?♫

18
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:47,440
♫I'm like searching in the abyss♫

19
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,780
♫For a lighthouse♫

20
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:53,020
So cold.

21
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:56,509
♫The path ahead still holds uncertainties♫

22
00:01:56,810 --> 00:01:58,810
♫It's hard to tell what's real from false♫

23
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,880
♫What I believed in was trampled at will♫

24
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:04,570
♫Dismissed as mere dreams and jokes♫

25
00:02:04,910 --> 00:02:09,250
♫If you want to escape this world, wait for the rain to fall♫

26
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,420
♫Watch the fireworks released by the gods♫

27
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,580
♫Just pause for a moment♫

28
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:16,140
♫Let the nearly barren heart sprout new buds♫

29
00:02:16,170 --> 00:02:18,020
♫Set forth again, and I won't be afraid♫

30
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:21,700
♫The most resilient flowers bloom on the cliffs♫

31
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:25,329
♫Let the past scars be carried away by the wind♫

32
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:28,860
♫Those who have dreams must first face♫

33
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:31,340
♫The chaos of the world♫

34
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:34,520
Young Master, we...

35
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:36,940
You go prepare the car. I'll be down shortly.

36
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:37,590
Okay.

37
00:02:58,180 --> 00:03:00,410
[Yu's Mansion]

38
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,490
So cold.

39
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:47,680
Who's there?

40
00:03:48,070 --> 00:03:48,790
Young Master, it's me.

41
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:50,340
What is it?

42
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:51,940
I just heard from Xiang

43
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,160
that Captain Wu has led his men

44
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:54,360
to cause trouble for Miss Lin tonight.

45
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:58,030
Wu You went after Lin Wanyue?

46
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:01,430
Is he still trying to force Miss Lin to give

47
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,750
a false statement accusing me of murder?

48
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:04,970
No.

49
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,380
I have to go there now.

50
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,960
Cheng Hao, get the car ready immediately.

51
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,800
Yes, Young Master.

52
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,350
Open the door!

53
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:17,950
Lin Wanyue!

54
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,370
You knew Yu Yanchuan was the murderer

55
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,269
of the Zhong Cheng couple,

56
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,720
yet you deliberately chose not to identify him.

57
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,190
Open the door!

58
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,270
Open the door!

59
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:42,920
Search this place!

60
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,600
Yes, sir!

61
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,800
Boss, she is not here.

62
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,640
The dog is still here.

63
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,360
Lin Wanyue must not have run away yet.

64
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,430
Keep searching.

65
00:05:17,580 --> 00:05:18,070
Yes.

66
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:44,630
Miss Lin.

67
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,230
There you are.

68
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,390
What do you want?

69
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:50,650
What can we, the police, do?

70
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,110
Of course, we're here to have you help investigate

71
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,080
the Zhong Cheng couple's murder case.

72
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,920
Haven't I already identified that man?

73
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,909
You're still trying to fool me?

74
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,650
You knew full well Yu Yanchuan was the one who murdered

75
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,680
the Zhong Cheng couple,

76
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,940
yet you deliberately didn't identify him.

77
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,470
He's not the murderer.

78
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:08,870
Fine.

79
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:10,390
Still being all stubborn, huh?

80
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,070
Before this rope breaks,

81
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,730
if you say Yu Yanchuan is the murderer,

82
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:19,950
I guarantee

83
00:06:20,470 --> 00:06:21,560
you'll live.

84
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,520
But if you don't...

85
00:06:24,730 --> 00:06:26,970
you'll be taking a one-way trip to the afterlife.

86
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:28,910
You're abusing your power

87
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,030
to extract a statement!

88
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:32,430
Even if it's so,

89
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,210
what can you do about it?

90
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,390
Don't push me any further.

91
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:41,510
Alright.

92
00:06:42,050 --> 00:06:44,240
Let's see how much longer you can hold on.

93
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,360
Help.

94
00:06:58,860 --> 00:06:59,600
Lin Wanyue!

95
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:17,400
♫I push hard to topple the darkness♫

96
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,780
♫A corner of light emerges♫

97
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,780
♫You spread your wings♫

98
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,130
Wanyue, grip my arm tightly.

99
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,030
♫Dancing quietly♫

100
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:32,340
♫You've been through surging waves♫

101
00:07:32,370 --> 00:07:34,700
♫Sending out signals♫

102
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:38,620
♫I say, in this world♫

103
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:41,960
♫There's still some beauty♫

104
00:07:43,490 --> 00:07:47,920
♫The night sky is upside down, with gentle hues♫

105
00:07:48,010 --> 00:07:51,560
♫If love could be the cure♫

106
00:07:51,710 --> 00:07:55,470
♫I'd search for you, for what was once lost♫

107
00:07:55,690 --> 00:07:58,720
♫Those playful jokes♫

108
00:07:59,610 --> 00:08:04,800
♫Waiting until you're ready to touch the heartbeat of the world♫

109
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:07,740
♫It's also a sign of me rushing toward you♫

110
00:08:07,770 --> 00:08:14,110
♫As the ice and snow melt away, I wait for your embrace♫

111
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:15,780
Mr. Yu, where are you taking me?

112
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:19,700
♫Waiting for the rainbow to stretch across every path♫

113
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:16,590
Miss Lin.

114
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:18,380
It's fine now.

115
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,180
Your place is not safe anymore.

116
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:23,370
♫And in your world, there is no more noise♫

117
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:21,330
Come stay at my place for now.

118
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,530
What?

119
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:28,090
♫I'm here, and you'll eventually feel it♫

120
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:24,480
Don't worry.

121
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:26,140
Only if you stay with me

122
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:28,120
will Wu You leave you alone.

123
00:08:31,730 --> 00:08:32,530
Alright.

124
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:34,450
Thank you, Mr. Yu.

125
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:03,720
Miss, Yu Yanchuan is here.

126
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:04,760
Okay.

127
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:06,610
Let's do it.

128
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:17,920
Miss,

129
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,980
I've already had Xiang spread the word.

130
00:09:20,450 --> 00:09:21,060
Okay.

131
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,410
Recently, Yu Zhenhai's butler, Lai Guangsheng,

132
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,550
has been watching us.

133
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:26,400
He's downstairs right now.

134
00:09:27,010 --> 00:09:28,250
Let's give him something drastic

135
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,790
to see.

136
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:30,420
Yes, Miss.

137
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:51,950
Father!

138
00:09:52,070 --> 00:09:52,790
Mother!

139
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,300
Master.

140
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,480
What should we do about Jiang Yude's daughter?

141
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:44,930
[Yu's Mansion]

142
00:10:47,690 --> 00:10:49,450
Hell may have taken my sight,

143
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,090
but it helped me return as an avenging ghost.

144
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:53,850
This time,

145
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,520
it's your turn to go to hell,

146
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,370
my enemies.
